General.Name: Clean Industry Solutions Holding Europe AB
General.GicIndustry: Independent Power and Renewable Electricity Producers
General.Description: Clean Industry Solutions Holding Europe AB, a technology and solution provider, develops solar power projects based on Fresnel collector technology in Sweden. The company offers LF-11 Fresnel solar collectors for industrial process heat applications. It also provides turnkey solutions for various industries, such as food, pharmaceutical, chemical, metal, automotive, etc. Clean Industry Solutions Holding Europe AB was founded in 2008 and is headquartered in Johanneshov, Sweden.
